data.description: Reduced for quick sale. Will appraise at 600k. Lovely home, excellent condition. Warm inviting floor plan, cathedral ceilings, snack bar with eat in kitchen. Garage converted to a cool man-cave/game room. Can be reconverted to a garage easily. Big backyard. Wheelchair accessible. No issues, no HOA, no rental restrictions. Motivated. Airbnb suitable.  Room for a pool.   Private wholesale financing available for qualified buyers with as little as 3.5%-10% down and rates as low as 5.27%.
